  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 64",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Jon VIII</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n714 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_55\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 55\">Jon VII</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_63\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 63\">Davos VI</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jon VIII</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_65\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 65\">Arya XII</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_69\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 69\">Jon IX</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_64&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The remaining members of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a> and several people from <a href=\"/index.php/Mole%27s_Town\" title=\"Mole&#39;s Town\">Mole's Town</a> man the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance</a>’s army approaches. As the Watch repels attack after attack from their great vantage point, some of the <a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">wildlings</a> have reach the gate. To his surprise, <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a> is left in command as <a href=\"/index.php/Donal_Noye\" title=\"Donal Noye\">Donal Noye</a> leaves to defend the gate. Jon orders fire arrows and oil casks dropped on the <a href=\"/index.php/Giants\" title=\"Giants\">giants</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Mammoth\" title=\"Mammoth\">mammoths</a>, and the defenders once again repel the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_beneath_the_Wall\" title=\"Battle beneath the Wall\">wildling attack</a>. In the aftermath of the fighting, Jon goes down into the gate tunnel, to find Donal Noye dead alongside <a href=\"/index.php/Mag_Mar_Tun_Doh_Weg\" title=\"Mag Mar Tun Doh Weg\">Mag Mar Tun Doh Weg</a>. When Jon tells Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon</a> the news, the ancient <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a> tells him that he must lead the Watch now.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Battle_of_Castle_Black_by_Giliberti.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Battle_of_Castle_Black_by_Giliberti.jpg/300px-Battle_of_Castle_Black_by_Giliberti.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Battle_of_Castle_Black_by_Giliberti.jpg/450px-Battle_of_Castle_Black_by_Giliberti.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/65/Battle_of_Castle_Black_by_Giliberti.jpg/600px-Battle_of_Castle_Black_by_Giliberti.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Battle_of_Castle_Black_by_Giliberti.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_beneath_the_Wall\" title=\"Battle beneath the Wall\">Battle beneath the Wall</a> by Giliberti</div></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List\">Character List</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_64&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance Rayder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Donal_Noye\" title=\"Donal Noye\">Donal Noye</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mag_Mar_Tun_Doh_Weg\" title=\"Mag Mar Tun Doh Weg\">Mag Mar Tun Doh Weg</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cellador\" title=\"Cellador\">Septon Cellador</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hareth_(Mole%27s_Town)\" title=\"Hareth (Mole&#39;s Town)\">Hareth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Satin\" title=\"Satin\">Satin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pyp\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pyp\">Pyp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grenn\" title=\"Grenn\">Grenn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Owen_the_Oaf\" title=\"Owen the Oaf\">Owen the Oaf</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_64&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mole%27s_Town\" title=\"Mole&#39;s Town\">Mole's Town</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">Wildlings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Giant\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Giant\">Giants</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mammoth\" title=\"Mammoth\">Mammoths</a></li></ul>\n</div> \n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_64&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from Aol member vbkorik27 previously at<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080228051425/members.aol.com/vbkorik27/summary/legend.html\">[1]</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2013/08/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-39\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Storm of Swords, Part 39</a>. Analyses and summary of the chapter by Leigh Butler.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403105644\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.049 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.201 seconds\nPreprocessor vi